Summary: I watch a lot of movies and I cannot wait for the next one to come along and tell me what's going to be interesting about it. Unfortunately this movie has none of these features.
Review: I watch a lot of movies and I like to give them all a chance just in case there is something interesting or exciting to warrant a viewing Unfortunately this movie has none of these features it is pointless and offers nothing in the way of story line,acting or direction The plot is non-existent with the actors just going through the motions and the dialogue is sooo boring its embarrassing. I wish the previous reviewers had posted earlier as this would have saved me 95 mins of my time
